<HEADLINE>
<P>
RITCHIE VALENS TO GET WALK OF FAME STAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ritchie Valens, the late rock legend, will be honored next May with a star on 
the Hollywood Boulevard Walk of Fame. 
</P>
<P>
The Pacoima youth, whose real name was Richard Valenzuela, rose to fame in the 
1950s. Valens, whose story was depicted in the film "La Bamba," died at age 17 
in a 1959 Iowa plane crash. 
</P>
</TEXT>
