<HEADLINE>
<P>
LEONA HELMSLEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Leona Helmsley, hotel queen, probably got what she deserves ("Hotel 'Queen' 
Helmsley Convicted of Tax Fraud," Part I, Aug. 31). As they say: "She got her 
comeuppance." Now if Uncle Sam can collect from all the other "tax cheaters" 
perhaps our large national debt can be made to look more respectable. Should we 
say about $85 billion more respectable? 
</P>
<P>
MONROE RUBINGER 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
