above, the stuffed peppers, below, and the meat loaf, right, are all candidates 
for simple good home- cooking that stretches the family budget. ; Photo, 
Chinese Beef Casserole is a buffet table favorite. The mixture can be assembled 
ahead of time and heated for just 25 minutes before serving to guests. RICK 
MEYER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
