champion, kicks at opponent in all-out combat at Hollywood Palladium. ; Photo, 
Kick-boxer Kathy Long displays muscles and championship belt after fight with 
Pixie Elmore. RICARDO DeARATANHA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Rock star David 
Lee Roth, hands raised, encourages kick-boxers. ; Photo, Fighter Ricky Valentin 
displays his mongoose tattoo in the dressing room. 
</P>
