CONFLICT OF INTEREST; LOS ANGELES CITY ATTORNEY; LOS ANGELES CITY TREASURER; 
RITTENBERG, LEONARD; FAR EAST NATIONAL BANK; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT 
OFFICIALS; MISMANAGEMENT; FORGERY; DOCUMENTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
