<P>
REDEVELOPMENT DIRECTOR HIRES FORMER COLLEAGUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Susan Shick, executive director of the Long Beach Redevelopment Agency, has 
brought a former colleague on board as her redevelopment project officer. She 
is Barbara Knight, who has been acting director of the Glendale Redevelopment 
Agency since Shick left that position earlier this year. 
</P>
<P>
Knight, who was an unsuccessful candidate to be Shick's permanent replacement 
in Glendale, will come to Long Beach to fill a position formerly occupied by 
Raul Escobedo, who left recently to accept a job in the private sector. 
</P>
<P>
Knight worked for Glendale for more than seven years before announcing her 
resignation last week. 
</P>
