<TEXT>
<P>
Switzerland has extradited to the United States the alleged ringleader of a 
scheme to extort $10 million from the E.I. du Pont de Nemours &amp; Co., Swiss 
authorities said today. 
</P>
<P>
Bruno Skerianz, who has dual citizenship in Argentina and Italy, was turned 
over to U.S. marshals in Geneva and flown to the United States, the Swiss 
Justice Department said. 
